    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tech Hustle</strong>是一款疯狂且节奏紧凑的管理模拟游戏，你将把一家小小的科技店打造成繁荣的帝国！一边处理送货，一边和顾客讨价还价，雇佣古怪的员工，并升级为全自动机器人管理一切——你则可以悠闲地喝杯咖啡。但要小心！黑市上有稀有科技产品的诱人交易……如果你愿意打破一些规则的话。你会选择稳妥行事，还是铤而走险登上巅峰？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/2eea5ace3a3ba9d572f7ecb47fb6528c.poster.avif?t=1759885708\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/2eea5ace3a3ba9d572f7ecb47fb6528c.webm?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/2eea5ace3a3ba9d572f7ecb47fb6528c.mp4?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经营线上和实体店铺</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/8eea2c608dc20ad4b9994f91b25cdbe5.poster.avif?t=1759885708\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/8eea2c608dc20ad4b9994f91b25cdbe5.webm?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/8eea2c608dc20ad4b9994f91b25cdbe5.mp4?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义店铺</strong>：将你的店铺打造成华丽或搞笑的风格——选择权在你！但要做好心理准备，迎接这样的顾客评价：“价格很棒，但那些霓虹厕所是怎么回事？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/c48646a60eca71d0dcd1189d8ba37518.poster.avif?t=1759885708\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/c48646a60eca71d0dcd1189d8ba37518.webm?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/c48646a60eca71d0dcd1189d8ba37518.mp4?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>订购产品并在线上和实体店销售</strong>：同时管理两个店铺，享受双倍的乐趣与混乱——毕竟，谁不喜欢一边处理促销，一边应对退款邮件呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/d6bb0a74f309b7ebdf4cbf89f9138fc1.poster.avif?t=1759885708\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/d6bb0a74f309b7ebdf4cbf89f9138fc1.webm?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/d6bb0a74f309b7ebdf4cbf89f9138fc1.mp4?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>配送系统</strong>：有货车吗？太棒了！现在赶紧穿越车流把订单送到客户手中，赶在他们抗议之前！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/66e3409f78d324123234aa30af04f708.poster.avif?t=1759885708\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/66e3409f78d324123234aa30af04f708.webm?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/66e3409f78d324123234aa30af04f708.mp4?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无人机配送</strong>：有了无人机，谁还需要驾驶执照呢？虽然有时能顺利送达包裹，但有时也会撞上树！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <br>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/30438091beb0a0962f929de3ee2e2e3a.poster.avif?t=1759885708\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/30438091beb0a0962f929de3ee2e2e3a.webm?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/30438091beb0a0962f929de3ee2e2e3a.mp4?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>实时昼夜系统</strong>：白天看着你的店铺热闹起来，夜晚则变得诡异安静……除了那个逛到凌晨3点的奇怪顾客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/f92240a675ce9d9f47e503e1e5852cf1.poster.avif?t=1759885708\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/f92240a675ce9d9f47e503e1e5852cf1.webm?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077220/extras/f92240a675ce9d9f47e503e1e5852cf1.mp4?t=1759885708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态天气</strong>：无论是晴天还是雨天，顾客都需要科技产品！只要做好准备，当送货无人机被困在雷雨中时应对自如。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造与扩展</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不同类型的车辆进行配送</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机器人全面自动化</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高风险的黑市交易</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非法风险任务获取轻松收益</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态市场事件</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实的 Unreal Engine 5 画面</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家与 AI 的盗窃系统</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作玩法 (CO-OP)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开放世界地图</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加到愿望单，随时获取最新消息。  </p>",
